Title: Man in Outer Space
Writer: Oldrich Lipský (story), Oldrich Lipský (screenplay), Zdenek Bláha, Jan Fiser, Milos Fiala
Actors: Milos Kopecký, Radovan Lukavský, Anita Kajlichova, Vít Olmer
Plot: A workman is accidentally sent into outer space, where he meets an alien that can make himself invisible. They return to Earth in the year 2447. Complications ensue.
